<h1>About Us</h1>
<p>TechFair is completely <strong>student run</strong>, led by passionate and dedicated students at the Massachusetts Institute of Technology. Members of the board are split into seven committees: Corporate Relations, Finance, Human Resources, Information Technology, Logistics, Marketing, and <a href="http://http://mittechfair.org/think/">THINK</a>.</p>
<h3>We are <span style="color:black">40 committee members</span> led by <span style="color:black">6 exec members</span> determined to throw<br /> <span style="color:black;font-size:30px">1 awesome event</span>.</h3>
